  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem; visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;background-color:transparent;font-variant-alternates:normal;visibility:visible;font-variant-emoji:normal;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-variant-east-asian:normal;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-position:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">今天，FlashLabs 正式发布&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Chroma 1.0 ——全球首个开源的支持声音克隆、高保真、端到端、实时语音到语音（Speech-to-Speech）AI 模型</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，并逐步部署于&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:transparent;text-decoration-line:underline;font-variant-alternates:normal;visibility:visible;font-variant-emoji:normal;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-variant-east-asian:normal;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-position:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">FlashAI</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">语音智能体平台。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;visibility: visible;\"><b style=\"font-weight: normal;visibility: visible;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;visibility:visible;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Chroma 是一个研究级、完全开源的实时语音模型，定位为 OpenAI Realtime API 的开放替代方案，面向全球开发者、研究者与企业用户。</span></span></span></b></p>\n  <b style=\"font-weight: normal;visibility: visible;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><b style=\"font-weight: normal;visibility: visible;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"> \n    <h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;margin-top: 14pt;margin-bottom: 4pt;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;visibility:visible;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:13pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🚨 Chroma 1.0 有什么不同？</span></span></span></h3> \n    <span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;visibility:visible;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">与传统「ASR → LLM → TTS」多阶段管线不同，</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;visibility:visible;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Chroma 原生支持语音到语音的端到端建模</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;visibility:visible;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，在延迟、自然度与一致性上实现突破式提升。</span></span></span> \n   </b> \n   <p style=\"text-align: center;visibility: visible;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100002934\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=736ebe9f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2G4CSGWj0b1IxAq3ftomIgK1DFGiacDdaMTe2mMEDviciarZxqkd1WKBichDmICOTwNgic9bVZDkkucTwNusTuED7NQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p> \n   <p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">核心亮点</span></span></p> \n   <b style=\"font-weight:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"> \n    <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:16px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;padding-left:18px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">⚡&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">端到端首字节延迟（TTFT）&lt; 150ms</span></span></span></b></strong></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🎙️</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">原生Speech-to-Speech架构</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（非拼接式流水线）</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🧬</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">几秒参考音频即可完成高保真声音克隆</span></span></strong></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">📈</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">SIM相似度=0.817</span></span></strong></p>\n     </li>\n     <ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px;padding-left: 18px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">相比人类基线（0.73）提升</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">+10.96%</span></span></strong></p>\n      </li>\n      <li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在已测试的开源与闭源模型中表现领先</span></span></p>\n      </li>\n     </ul>\n     <li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🧠</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">仅4B参数即具备强对话与推理能力</span></span></strong></p>\n     </li>\n     <ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px;padding-left: 18px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">基于Qwen2.5-Omni-3B、Llama 3、Mimi等架构优化</span></span></p>\n      </li>\n     </ul>\n     <li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🔓</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">完全开源（代码+权重）</span></span></strong></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul> \n    <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:16px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Chroma在发布当天即支持</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">SGLang推理框架</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，用于高并发、低延迟实时语音场景：</span></span></p> \n    <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:16px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;padding-left:18px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🧠Thinker TTFT再降</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">≈15%</span></span></strong></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">⏱️端到端TTFT低至</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">≈135ms</span></span></strong></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 0px !important;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🔊实时因子（RTF）≈</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">0.47–0.51</span></span></strong></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul> \n   </b> \n   <h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 14pt;margin-bottom: 4pt;\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:13pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🌍 面向未来的实时语音 AI 基础模型</span></span></span></h3> \n   <p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 12pt;margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Chroma 1.0 的发布，标志着</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">实时语音 AI 正式进入“开源 + 端到端 + 低延迟”的新阶段</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span></span><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;它不仅适用于&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">AI 呼叫中心、语音客服、销售外呼、虚拟人、实时翻译</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;等场景，也为研究者提供了一个可复现、可扩展的基础模型。</span></span></span></p> \n   <p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 12pt;margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">FlashLabs 相信：</span></span></span></p> \n   <p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 12pt 30pt;\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">语音将成为 AI 时代最重要的人机接口，而实时性是决定体验的关键。</span></span></span></p> \n   <p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 12pt;margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Chroma 1.0 让开源社区首次拥有能够与顶级闭源产品相媲美的语音实时端到端、高保真生成能力。</span></span></span></p> \n   <h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 14pt;margin-bottom: 4pt;\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:13pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🔗 了解更多</span></span></span></h3> \n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding-inline-start: 48px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;list-style-type:disc;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">\n     <p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 12pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">产品部署：</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">FlashAI 语音智能体</span></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;list-style-type:disc;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">\n     <p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Paper &amp; Benchmarks:</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.11141\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.11141</a></span></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;list-style-type:disc;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">\n     <p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">开源代码与模型权重：</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family